                <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--grey-700); margin: 24px 0;">Partnering with Dell, Huawei, Apple, IBM, Microsoft, Cisco & leading certification bodies. We deliver enterprise hardware, global certifications, digital learning & bulk supply across Africa.</p>
                <div class="trust-badges">
